{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"24":"Wages (Kitab Al-Ijarah)"},"section_detail":{"24":{"hadithnumber_first":3416,"hadithnumber_last":3570,"arabicnumber_first":3416,"arabicnumber_last":3570}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3471,"arabicnumber":3471,"text":"Ata a dit : Le fléau, c’est tout ce qui endommage manifestement la récolte, comme la pluie, la grêle, les sauterelles, une rafale de vent ou le feu","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Maqtu"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Maqtu"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Maqtu"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":24,"hadith":56}}]}